.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-HISTORY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-history \- show forwarded payments through a channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-history
.RI [ channel_id ]
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the most recent forwarded payments (HTLCs) through a channel
from
.BR listforwards .
Without
.IR channel_id ,
returns history across all channels.
Default limit is 50.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{in_channel, out_channel, amount_msat, fee_msat,
  resolved_time, status}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-api-forward-stats (1),
.BR lightning-node-fee-revenue (1)
